Original:
2022/12/23，晚間初訪。

若不是特別為了跟久違的朋友在新莊吃一頓，沒有特別搜尋還真不 知道中港大排附近也是有間品質不錯的居酒屋。

網路上簡單看了一下評價，多為正面評價，菜單上面的價錢跟台北市的比起來是相對的親民，而且還提供酒類喝到飽的服務。不過我已經過了那種動不動就要豪飲的年紀了，簡單的點一壺清酒跟生啤就夠我們開心聊一個晚上了。

可惜由於老友遲到整整一小時，部分預先點好的很多菜送上來後都冷掉了，雖然風味略減，但味道調理依然適宜，只有炸物沒有立即吃掉，冷掉了就少了酥脆的口感。各種烤串熱呼呼的一口一串，搭配生啤酒非常過癮。炒烏龍麵還熱騰的時候有偷吃一口，熱氣使蛤蠣的鮮甜融入在麵內，非常滑順，後來冷掉了再吃，味道就差了一截了。只能下次學乖跟老友再約晚一點，省得只能對著一桌美食乾瞪眼，落得最後吃冷食。

兩人整體下來約莫花了共兩千初頭，分量點下來兩個人吃的也是剛剛好，沒有食物被浪費，酒足飯飽，也帶著一點快樂的微醺。下次應該還是會找時間回來，跟友人二度小酌一下。
EN:
2022/12/23, visit at the beginning of the evening.

If it wasn't for a long -lost friend to eat a meal in Xinzhuang, there was no special search, and I really didn't know that there was a good izakaya near the China and Hong Kong University.

I briefly read the evaluation on the Internet. Most of them are positive evaluations. The price on the menu is relatively close to the Taipei City, and it also provides the service of drinking to drink.But I have passed the age that I have to drink in every turn. Simply order a pot of sake to talk with raw beer enough for us to talk about it for a night.

Unfortunately, because the old friends are late for an hour, some of the pre -ordering dishes are cold and they have been cold. Although the flavor is slightly reduced, the taste conditioning is still suitable. Only the explosives are not eaten immediately. The taste.Various baked skewers are hot, with raw beer very enjoyable.When the oolong noodles were still hot, a sip was sneaked. The hot air merged the sweetness of the oysters into the face. It was very smooth. Later, it was cold and then ate, and the taste was worse.Only next time I can learn from my old friends to make an appointment a little later, saving can only stare at a table of food, and finally eat cold food.

The two spent about two thousand at the beginning of the two, and the two people were eaten by the two people. They were wasteful without food, full of wine, and a little happy.I should still find time to come back next time and have a drink with my friends.
